local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["menopause"]={"menopause","['menəpɔːz]","['mɛnə'pɔz]","n.停经期",'n.停经期,更年期','A period of life characterized by physiological and psychic change that marks the end of the reproductive capacity of women and terminates with the completion of menopause.','绝经期, 更年期生命的一个阶段, 特征是标志妇女生殖能力终结及以停经完成为结束的生理、心理变化','...alternative therapies to fight the symptoms of menopause.','…对抗更年期症状的替代疗法。'}
